User Stories

The following required functionality is completed:

[] User can sign up using email
 User can sign up using Twitter/Facebook to create a new account using Parse authentication
 User can log in and log out of his or her account
 The current signed in user is persisted across app restarts
 User can upload an item to their inventory on their own account
 User can view their "tags" and connect with a person who found their missing item
 user can view their current location on a map view upon hitting submit on the prompt screen
The following optional features are implemented:

 Show the username and creation time for each post
 After the user submits a new post, show a progress HUD while the post is being uploaded to Parse.
 User Profiles:
 Allow the logged in user to add a profile photo
 Display the profile photo with each post
 Tapping on a post's username or profile photo goes to that user's profile page
